      "uiColor": "red",
      "title": "Quick question first…",
      "question": "Two kettles both transfer 100 000 J to heat water. Kettle A takes 60 s and Kettle B takes 120 s. Which is more powerful?",
      "options": [
        "Kettle B (it takes longer so uses more power)",
        "They have the same power (same energy)",
        "Kettle A (it transfers the same energy in less time)",
        "It depends on the mass of water"
